mily:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:black\">&nbsp;&ndash; Step-by-step online guide through the Portal processes from proposal preparation and submission to reporting on your on-going project. Valid for all 2021-2027 programmes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"staticAdditionalInfo": "<p> </p><p><strong><u>Proposals are invited against the following topic</u>:</strong></p><ul level=\"0\"><li><strong>EDF-2022-LS-DA-SME-NT:</strong> Non-thematic development actions by SMEs</li> </ul>\n<p>The Union is considering a contribution of up to EUR 36 500 000 to support proposals addressing the above mentioned topic and its associated objectives, scope, targeted activities, functional requirements and expected impact, while considering a contribution of up to EUR 4 000 000 per proposal.</p>\n", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Sep 13, 2022 5:21:17 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Sep 13, 2022 5:21:17 PM", "content": "<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D\">New versions of detailed budget table for EDF LS DA.</span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D\"> <br />\r\nCorrection of formula for PESCO bonus in sheets Info [activities] (see tab &ldquo;history of changes&rdquo; in the file for more details).<u><o:p></o:p></u></span></p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Jun 21, 2022 12:52:08 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jun 21, 2022 12:52:08 PM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: EDF-2022-LS-DA-SME-NT(EDF-LS)"}, {"approvalDate": "Jun 10, 2022 4:57:06 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jun 10, 2022 4:57:06 PM", "content": "<div class=\"WordSection1\" style=\"page: WordSection1; font-size: medium;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;\">News update: hyperlinks to documents in </span><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Topic conditions and documents</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;\"> have been updated.</span></p>\r\n</div>"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}